  "response": "To create clothes in Roblox, you'll need to follow these steps:\n\n1. Create the design:\n- Use an image editing software like Photoshop, GIMP, or Paint.net\n- Design a template for shirts, pants, or t-shirts\n- Follow Roblox's specific template dimensions\n- Save the image as a .png file with a transparent background\n\n2. Upload the clothing:\n- Log into Roblox\n- Go to the \"Create\" page\n- Click on \"Develop\"\n- Select either \"Shirts\", \"Pants\", or \"T-Shirts\"\n- Upload your image file\n- Set a price if you want to sell it\n\n3. Publish the clothing:\n- Click \"Upload\" to make your clothing item available\n- It will now appear in your inventory and can be worn by your avatar\n\nTips:\n- Use high-quality, clear designs\n- Ensure the image fits the Roblox template\n- Keep file sizes small\n- Make sure your design follows Roblox's community guidelines\n\nYou'll need a Roblox Premium membership to sell clothing in the Roblox catalog.",
